                                    </dimensions>
                                    <seg type="pricking">Pricking does not survive. </seg>
                                    <seg type="ruling">Ruled in hardpoint, type Leroy <formula notation="Leroy">22D2a</formula>. The text appears in a
                                        variable relationship to the lines, but is mostly written
                                        along them.</seg>
                                </layout>
